originalText.text: I am absolutely blown away by how helpful the team here is! They literally bend over backwards to help their customers with such poise, friendliness, and comfort one could ever imagine from a storage space. Special shot-out to Anderson and DJ especially for being so capable and excellent at making PUBLIC Storage a flexible and easy-to-use option.

originalText.text:
Wish I could leave negative stars. If you are planing to use Public Storage- stay away from this place. I have few different storages in NY - no issues, this place gave me nightmares. They had glitch in the system- so for the past 3 months I have been receiving calls, messages emails that my payment is pass due, they send me two refund checks for $15 that makes no sense, added extra unit to my account ( I own just one small unit) - that was $28 dollars of past due - kept on calling me daily to pay.
I went in person five times and talked to the management - they assure me not to worry, my account is fine and it was their error.
When I tried to access my unit - I count not - they blocked my access. Takes to the management and they let me in saying I have nothing to worry about- they will fix it. 3 months after - I still get calls from Public Storage asking to pay bill - and now I have debt collector calling me for $28 filed from Public Storage. I have never had past due bill in my life, I have perfect credit score I worked my whole life for and now thanks to this place - It’s ruined. I have to keep on calling and fixing this but if you have not get unit here - save yourself and go somewhere else.

As a long-time customer of this storage facility, I must say that my experience has been nothing short of fantastic. The staff, especially DJ, has consistently provided exceptional service throughout the years. Their dedication and attentiveness have made my storage journey smooth and hassle-free.

The facility's top-notch maintenance and security have further solidified my trust in them. They recently upgraded the security system. I highly recommend this place to anyone in need of storage solutions, and I'm grateful for DJ and the team's continued outstanding support!
